{"lemma":"طَيُّ","slug":"طَيُّ","root":"ط.#.#","root_slug":"ط-_-_","root_link":"/words/roots/ط-_-_","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"طَيُّ","root":"طوي","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":4},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n27379","n27380","n27401"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B7%D9%8E%D9%8A%D9%8F%D9%91"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of طَوَى (ṭawā) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"fold, plica"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"often meaning that something is included within or attached with","examples":[{"text":"فِي طَيِّ ٱلنِّسْيَانِ","english":"into oblivion"},{"text":"فِي طَيِّ ٱلْكِتْمَانِ","english":"secretly"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"concealment, hiddenness"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/tˤajj/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n27379","headword_ar":"طَىٌّ","root":"TwY","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[originally an inf. n., of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TawaY","text_ar":"طَوَى"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.,] and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TiY~N","text_ar":"طِىٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TiwaY","text_ar":"طِوَى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", [said in one place in the TA to be like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ilaY","text_ar":"اـِلَى"},{"kind":"text","text":", but I think that this is only said to show that its first vowel is kesr and the second fet-h, and that it is correctly"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TiwFY","text_ar":"طِوًى"},{"kind":"text","text":", for there is no reason for its being imperfectly decl.,] accord. to"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1899},{"kind":"text","text":"the M, are sings. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aTowaA='N","text_ar":"اَطْوَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which it explains as signifying The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lines,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"streaks,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"creases, of the folding"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a garment, or piece of cloth, and of a written piece of paper, and of the belly, and of fat, and of the guts, and of a serpent, and of other things; and it is said in the T and K that ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maTaAwK","text_ar":"مَطَاوٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", of which the sing. is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maTowFY","text_ar":"مَطْوًى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", signifies the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aTowaA='","text_ar":"اَطْوَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the serpent, and of the guts, and of fat, and of the belly, and of a garment, or piece of cloth: (TA:) one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^amaEaAy^ihaA","text_ar":"اَمَعَايِهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA baqiyato fiY maTaAwiY","text_ar":"مَا بَقِيَتْ فِى مَطَاوِى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vamiylapN","text_ar":"ثَمِيلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There remained not in the creases of her,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"their, guts any relic of food"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (A, TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ald~iroEi","text_ar":"الدِّرْعِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maTaAwiY","text_ar":"مَطَاوِى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the creases of the coat of mail when it is drawn together,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contracted."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [Hence,] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY jabiynihaA A^aTowaA='u Aln~ajomi","text_ar":"عَلَى جَبِينِهَا اَطْوَا=ءُ النَّجْمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaraAy^iquhu","text_ar":"طَرَايِقُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Upon her forehead"},{"kind":"text","text":"(for so"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jabiyn","text_ar":"جَبِين"},{"kind":"text","text":"sometimes signifies)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"are the wrinkles indicative of the time for the payment of the debt of nature"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aTowaA='","text_ar":"اَطْوَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the she-camel are The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaraAy^iq","text_ar":"طَرَايِق"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lines,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"streaks,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or perhaps"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"creases,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wrinkles,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the fat"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the hump:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) [or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"creases,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wrinkles, one above another, of the side"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the hump;"},{"kind":"text","text":"for] Lth says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaraAy^iqu janobihaA wasanaAmhaA TaY~N fawoqa TaY~K","text_ar":"طَرَايِقُ جَنْبِهَا وَسَنَامهَا طَىٌّ فَوْقَ طَىٍّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the creases,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wrinkles, of her side and of her hump are,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"consist of,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaY~","text_ar":"طَىّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"above"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaY~","text_ar":"طَىّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And AHn says that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aTowaA='N","text_ar":"اَطْوَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bending"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or rather he should have said, or perhaps he did say, the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"places of bending"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the tail of the locust,"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which are"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Euqad","text_ar":"عُقَد"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"articulations"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and the pl. [of mult.] is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TiwaY","text_ar":"طِوَى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[said to be like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ilaY","text_ar":"اـِلَى"},{"kind":"text","text":", but I think that it is correctly"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TiwFY","text_ar":"طِوًى"},{"kind":"text","text":", as I have observed above]. (TA.) ―         -b2-  One says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wajadotu fiY TaY~i","text_ar":"وَجَدْتُ فِى طَىِّ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlkitaAbi ka*aA","text_ar":"الكِتَابِ كَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I found within the folding of the writing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"letter, such a thing;"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"infolded,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"enclosed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"included, in it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"among the contents,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"implications, of it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY A^aTowaA='i","text_ar":"فِى اَطْوَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alkutubi","text_ar":"الكُتُبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maTaAwiyhaA","text_ar":"مَطَاوِيهَا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"within the folds,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"places of folding, of the writings,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"letters"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Algil~u fiY TaY~i qalobihi","text_ar":"الغِلُّ فِى طَىِّ قَلْبِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Rancour, malevolence, malice,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"spite, is conceived, as though it were infolded, in his heart"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA. [See 7.]) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adorajaniY fiY TaY~i Aln~isoyaAni","text_ar":"اَدْرَجَنِى فِى طَىِّ النِّسْيَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, infolded me within the folding of oblivion"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b3-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TawFY","text_ar":"طَوًى"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b4-  And see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TawiY~N","text_ar":"طَوِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b5-  [Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A casing of stones"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of baked bricks; and"},{"kind":"text","text":"particularly such a casing of a well; an inf. n. used as a subst. properly so called; and often occurring in the lexicons &c. in this sense.]"}],"source_refs":["TA","A","S","K"]},{"entry_id":"n27380","headword_ar":"طِىٌّ","root":"TwY","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the next preceding paragraph, first sentence."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n27401","headword_ar":"طَىَّ","root":"TY","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TiY~N","text_ar":"طِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tay~apN","text_ar":"طَيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tiy~apN","text_ar":"طِيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(also pronounced"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TiyapN","text_ar":"طِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"): and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tay~aAnu","text_ar":"طَيَّانُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", fem."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tay~aA","text_ar":"طَيَّا"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tay~aA='N","text_ar":"طَيَّا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TwY","text_ar":"طوى"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}